name: Kicking Across Carolina (Official Shirt) - Blue
description: These are the official shirts for Kicking Across Carolina. Kicking Across Carolina is a brand new initiative, where 3 UNC-Chapel Hill Students will attempt to dribble 410 miles across the state of North Carolina. Made by Eurosport and their Kickback Program, 100% of the sales goes to support peaceful co-existence in the war-torn regions of the Israel and Palestine. ------ Please be patient as we are dribbling across North Carolina, we are traveling with the shirts and will not be able to ship them regularly. Printed on Gildan Ultra Cotton / Preshrunk / 100% Cotton Click Here For More Info
